    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has extensive rust, several large dents, and peeling paint. The interior is in bad shape with ripped seats and a non-functional dashboard. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and the transmission slips.",
