    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips typical of regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of any major tears or stains. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. While it isn't in showroom condition, it is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready to drive immediately.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior suffers from significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with various dents and a failing clear coat. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul, and there are several fluid leaks that need immediate attention. The interior is heavily worn with torn seats and some non-functional dashboard components, making this an ideal candidate for a parts donor or a very ambitious restoration project.",
      "price": 4700.0,
